    <title>黄瓜</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/2020-06-28-%E9%BB%84%E7%93%9C/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/2020-06-28-%E9%BB%84%E7%93%9C/</id>
    <published>2020-06-28T07:14:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-30T14:51:34.132Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>黄瓜炒香肠—黄瓜和香肠切好，起锅烧油，放蒜爆香然后锅中加入切好的黄瓜和香肠翻炒大约一分钟左右，放入盐再翻炒一会就可以出锅了。</p><p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/f7ff0bfcd82ef02e26bb13d2.html?picindex=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e57a258602214f57ae09350e732064fb970b73f4.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1" alt="黄瓜菜的做法"></a></p><p>炒黄瓜—起锅烧油，蒜末爆香，倒入黄瓜片，翻炒均匀，炒一分钟左右放入盐调味即可，既简单又美味。</p><p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/f7ff0bfcd82ef02e26bb13d2.html?picindex=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/f9617afb960b3121463e6216dee983aee9d76df4.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1" alt="黄瓜菜的做法"></a></p><p>黄瓜炒鸡蛋—准备鸡蛋和黄瓜，锅内倒入油之后撒入鸡蛋，鸡蛋成块时倒入碗里，再加适量油，葱花爆香放入黄瓜翻炒，加入鸡蛋继续翻炒，出锅前放盐就可以了。</p><p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/f7ff0bfcd82ef02e26bb13d2.html?picindex=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/e996472ae3efe0785f6eb903b96c576698cf65f4.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1" alt="黄瓜菜的做法"></a></p><p>拍黄瓜—黄瓜洗净，不用去皮，用刀拍扁然后切成块，放入醋、酱油、鸡精、盐、糖，蒜蓉，香菜等调料搅拌机均匀，盛入碗里即可。</p><p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/f7ff0bfcd82ef02e26bb13d2.html?picindex=4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/2e223d85e036e29112b75555b2723d03baea5bf4.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1" alt="黄瓜菜的做法"></a></p><p>腌黄瓜—黄瓜洗净晾干水分，撒上盐，腌三个小时控净水分备用。锅里倒入水放入适量糖将黄瓜和陈醋放在一起煮开，晾凉，放到容器里腌七天就可以吃了。</p><p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/f7ff0bfcd82ef02e26bb13d2.html?picindex=5" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/6002c9d4483104eb96f839ba092b74ee1d324ef4.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1" alt="黄瓜菜的做法"></a></p><p>凉拌黄瓜—黄瓜切丝，拉皮用水浸泡，碗里放入醋、糖、酱油、香油、蒜末，加入切好的黄瓜丝和拉皮拌均匀即可。</p><p><a href="http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/f7ff0bfcd82ef02e26bb13d2.html?picindex=6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-src="https://exp-picture.cdn.bcebos.com/8db0c6a726334884a6bc2d99ddee7b7f870e45f4.jpg?x-bce-process=image%2Fresize%2Cm_lfit%2Cw_500%2Climit_1" alt="黄瓜菜的做法"></a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;黄瓜炒香肠—黄瓜和香肠切好，起锅烧油，放蒜爆香然后锅中加入切好的黄瓜和香肠翻炒大约一分钟左右，放入盐再翻炒一会就可以出锅了。&lt;/p&gt;
